WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:08.448
Hey, good morning family. How are y'all doing? It's evening here now, but I always say good morning because it's morning somewhere.

00:00:08.449 --> 00:00:14.555
I always come here to this campus because of what the Lord has showed me is coming here.

00:00:14.556 --> 00:00:19.649
And these praying hands when I drive by, they mean so much to me.

00:00:19.650 --> 00:00:28.574
You know, the motto of the school is 'Make no little plans here.'This is the ORU campus, by the way.

00:00:28.575 --> 00:00:37.524
I was driving by tonight and the Holy Spirit was just stirring in me so strong about the revival that's about to take place at this campus.

00:00:37.525 --> 00:00:47.069
You know, it's just what faith will build, what faith will do when you use your faith like a muscle.

00:00:47.070 --> 00:00:53.233
It's important, y'all. I drive by this because it inspires me to think big.

00:00:53.234 --> 00:00:58.349
It inspires me because this is what Oral Roberts believed God for.

00:00:58.350 --> 00:01:04.205
Every day I try to drive around here at least once and try to come over here and just inspire myself.

00:01:04.206 --> 00:01:20.129
The towers over there where the hospital was—I know they've sold that recently, I believe—but just the center, because the Lord showed me there will be a major outpouring of the spirit of the Lord in that big coliseum once again.

00:01:20.130 --> 00:01:27.199
The old wells of revival are coming uncapped. He told me, and I come over and I look at the prayer tower.

00:01:27.200 --> 00:01:34.557
Can you see the prayer tower over there? The prayer tower right there—it's right over there. That's where they pray.

00:01:34.558 --> 00:02:04.906
And I just thought, you know, it's exciting because some of the greatest ministers of any generation—I mean, I believe from Kathryn Kuhlman to Benny Hinn to all the greats that have come through here and had healing services and deliverance services where, you know, their ministry may not be all that it was back then, but look at what God did at one point in time through this right here.

00:02:04.907 --> 00:02:08.769
And what an amazing thing that he's doing and I know that he's going to do again.

00:02:08.770 --> 00:02:18.953
I showed you Victory and it's just right there. And I'm just excited because expectation brings manifestation. And it has nothing to even do with me.

00:02:18.954 --> 00:02:37.314
It's just something that I pray over because I know that God is going to visit the young generation, this young youth again with one last call, one last harvest, a major harvest of souls like we've never seen before and the glory of the Lord with fire.

00:02:37.315 --> 00:02:45.975
I believe that there'll be signs and wonders in the last days like it did with Azusa Street when there was a pillar of fire that was shown over Azusa Street.

00:02:45.976 --> 00:02:58.598
And I'm believing there'll be a pillar of fire over this Mabee Center and there'll be a pillar of fire over this ORU campus and that there will be a greater revival than even what happened at Asbury.

00:02:58.599 --> 00:03:14.225
You know that revival, I don't know, I guess it kind of fizzled out, but my goodness, I know that we're on the cusp of something huge about to take place in this Tulsa metroplex area and that God is about to do something huge in these last days.

00:03:14.226 --> 00:03:24.643
The Lord showed me Pastor Billy Joe Daugherty's son Paul Daugherty at that church right there, that there'll be an extension of the revival that's about to take place at ORU.

00:03:24.644 --> 00:03:35.078
And this is a massive church there, Victory. Well, Diana's with me now and it was so cold I had to get out of being outside.

00:03:35.079 --> 00:03:42.011
I told her, I said, 'I can't make this video.'I was trying to go and make the video at the campus and I was freezing.

00:03:42.012 --> 00:03:49.627
The wind was blowing so hard and it was cold and I told Braden, I said, 'Are you cold?'He goes, 'Yeah.'I said, 'I'm cold, too.

00:03:49.628 --> 00:03:59.438
Let's go.'So, you know, we have such an urgency though as we make the rest of this video for you all.

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:11.039
The things the Lord has been putting on our hearts is he said, 'Brandon, people are not awake yet. There's no sense of urgency.

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:22.630
Even in the upper leadership, they have a form of urgency, but deep down in their heart, there's not a stirring.'And people go, 'Well, you're judging people.'No, I'm not judging people.

00:04:22.631 --> 00:04:31.016
I'm just saying what he says. I have no idea what you feel, but I know what the Holy Spirit has told me, and I'm just going by what he said.

00:04:31.017 --> 00:04:38.313
So, if you don't agree with it, take it up with him. All I can say is what he's told me and what we pray about.

00:04:38.314 --> 00:04:48.370
And the Lord said, 'I'm going to bring a greater shaking to awaken beyond anybody's comprehension of what's about to happen, folks.

00:04:48.371 --> 00:04:58.556
I'm telling you, a major shaking.'And people go, 'Well, that sounds like fear.'You know, Diana and I are talking about a lot of the people that we've come in contact with.

00:04:58.557 --> 00:05:16.319
They say, 'Well, you're a fearmonger or whatever.'They've said that before to us in the past and maybe, just maybe, your channel has grown so much because you preach a lot of fear because fear sells.

00:05:16.320 --> 00:05:27.359
But folks, it's not fear. It's an awakening unto God. And if you're in fear, it's because you're not awake.

00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:35.536
Your heart should be looking vertical with him. And that shouldn't scare you whenever he said these things are going to happen because why?

00:05:35.537 --> 00:05:40.394
We're dead to self. We are looking for the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:05:40.395 --> 00:05:45.246
And we have an urgency. And he told me, he said, 'Brandon, there's no urgency.

00:05:45.247 --> 00:05:52.317
There's no urgency in my body. There's no urgency right now. Do you really realize I'm on my way?

00:05:52.317 --> 00:06:07.326
Do you really realize that this is the last call for the harvest of souls, the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen before?'As we sit on ORU campus with these hands, they mean something.

00:06:07.327 --> 00:06:18.507
They mean prayer changes things. They mean to me as I drive by it that somebody used their faith to get those hands there.

00:06:18.508 --> 00:06:25.076
That probably cost a lot of money. Behind us, that campus that you all seen, the Mabee Center, cost millions of dollars.

00:06:25.077 --> 00:06:41.686
It was Oral Roberts'faith that brought that forth using his faith like a tool—not a weapon, but a tool—a tool that he continually used to build his campus, to build the university for God.

00:06:41.687 --> 00:06:49.308
And he gave all the glory to God taking healing to the nations, raising up doctors, doing all the things that he did in his generation.

00:06:49.309 --> 00:06:57.464
But the Lord said, 'Brandon, there's one more wave. There's one more wave of revival.

00:06:57.465 --> 00:07:20.072
Those old wells that had been capped,'the Lord said, 'I capped them.'He said, 'I'm uncapping those wells.'And as you saw that church, Victory, he said, 'Brandon, there, Victory and ORU will be an extension of each other in the days ahead, and you will see a major outpouring of the spirit of the Lord greater than even Asbury.

00:07:20.073 --> 00:07:25.564
That was nothing compared to what's about to happen with that Mabee Center.

00:07:25.565 --> 00:07:32.314
That's nothing compared to what we're about to see all throughout Tulsa with Victory Church.

00:07:32.315 --> 00:07:37.584
That Victory Church across the street—I don't know how many seats that holds, probably a 10,000-seat auditorium.

00:07:37.585 --> 00:07:42.229
That's a massive one. And then they have the Mabee Center. And I don't know how many seats that holds.

00:07:42.230 --> 00:07:47.945
The Mabee Center is a little over 10,000 seats. Okay. So, you have 10,000 seats in the Mabee Center.

00:07:47.946 --> 00:07:53.986
Thanks, babe. Ten thousand seats in the Mabee Center. We have 5,000 at Victory Church.

00:07:53.987 --> 00:07:58.603
Okay. So, 15,000 seat capacity between the two. That's amazing.

00:07:58.604 --> 00:08:04.592
And they could do simulcast, make it live, have an overflow, but it doesn't matter when the glory is there.

00:08:04.593 --> 00:08:15.839
It's about a radical move of the spirit of God one last time. 'One last call,'he said.

00:08:15.840 --> 00:08:19.466
And now I see it. Do you remember I told you he was going to use the angels?

00:08:19.467 --> 00:08:24.659
He told me, he said, 'Brandon, I'm sending my reserves, my angel army reserves.

00:08:24.660 --> 00:08:27.995
I'm sending them.'There's going to be two angels per person.

00:08:27.996 --> 00:08:35.128
No matter how many demonic spirits there are on the earth, greater is he that is in you than he that is in the world.

00:08:35.129 --> 00:08:40.079
I was listening to Sister Billie talk about old stories and John G.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:52.398
Lake would go and he would put a beautiful white suit on with a white tie all fixed up every day because he saw himself as a carrier of the glory.

00:08:52.399 --> 00:09:07.242
He saw himself as someone who carried God to the nations. There were over 100,000 documented miracles that came through his ministry over the course of the whole time he was preaching.

00:09:07.243 --> 00:09:17.035
But he got radically on fire going to Azusa Street. There is a cross-pollination with the glory.

00:09:17.036 --> 00:09:27.994
As you are on fire, you light somebody else on fire. It's not going to be just about the churches, folks.

00:09:27.995 --> 00:09:41.919
God told me specifically that he was going to do something huge on the OU campus, that there would be a major healing revival come forth with the young people there.

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:54.460
So that's why I go and I pray and I drive around it. You go all down Lewis Avenue and I just circle around, just praying in the spirit, seeing the Lord show me something else.

00:09:54.461 --> 00:10:05.617
I'm hungry. I'm desperate. I want change. I am so tired of having church that's just normal.

00:10:05.618 --> 00:10:08.719
I know it's like, what are we looking for? What are we waiting for?

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:14.958
What is going to be the tipping point to what we're looking for?

00:10:14.959 --> 00:10:26.110
And the Lord said, "There's no urgency in my churches, for the coming of my son is at hand."Many believe it's way far off in the distant future.

00:10:26.111 --> 00:10:38.879
But I'm trying to tell you all, just like Paul Revere riding in the midnight hour telling you the British are coming, I'm writing in the midnight hour telling you that Jesus is coming as loud as I can.

00:10:38.880 --> 00:10:45.769
I've been there. I've seen it. I know exactly what the Lord is saying in my heart.

00:10:45.770 --> 00:10:50.630
He's shaking me to awaken me every day and have an expectation.

00:10:50.631 --> 00:11:01.088
I wake up with an urgency every single day to tell you all about the Lord, to tell you all there's a storm coming.

00:11:01.089 --> 00:11:05.011
I'm here to tell you all there's a heaven to gain and a hell to shun.

00:11:05.012 --> 00:11:27.751
I'm trying to wake you up to tell you all with urgency, to shake you until your teeth rattle, to tell you, "Listen to me, Jesus is coming."When I went through tribulation with him and he took me out of my body—I don't know if I was in my body or out of my body—I don't know what happened.

00:11:27.752 --> 00:11:36.370
All I know is I was there, and Jesus told me what was coming before he came.

00:11:36.371 --> 00:11:42.078
He told me there would be one major push that would not last that long.

00:11:42.079 --> 00:11:54.464
There would be a major revival that does not last that long, a glorious church that will rise up like Tommy Hicks'vision that he had.

00:11:54.465 --> 00:12:01.838
You can Google it—Tommy Hicks'vision—and see what I'm talking about, that the body would move like a mighty giant.

00:12:01.839 --> 00:12:10.719
But the Lord said to me, "Brandon, it's not about charismatics. It's not about the non-denominationalists.

00:12:10.720 --> 00:12:24.424
I'm going to pour out my spirit upon all flesh."Do you understand? It's going to be a denominational barrier buster.

00:12:24.425 --> 00:12:41.590
Where it's been, "Well, the Baptists are over here and we don't really listen to them because of their doctrine,"and "Well, we don't listen to the Catholics because of their doctrine,"and we've got the Methodists and we don't really know what they believe, or what the Church of Christ believe, or whoever.

00:12:41.591 --> 00:12:51.359
The Lord said, "I'm bringing these denominational walls down."He's going to break the walls down.

00:12:51.360 --> 00:13:11.274
And he told me, "We will move as a body."Yeah, we all have different thinking, but whenever wartime happened, like in World War II, the men were out to war and the women helped in the factories and did all the things they could to help support the men.

00:13:11.275 --> 00:13:23.979
Do you understand? In war times, in the body of Christ, we're a body, we're a family. It's not about religious barriers.

00:13:23.980 --> 00:13:33.759
It's about taking down those walls and knowing that it's all for one and one for all, like the Three Musketeers.

00:13:33.760 --> 00:13:41.382
We're going to do something big for Jesus. It's about getting the lost saved.

00:13:41.383 --> 00:13:58.662
We have differences of thinking, but we all have the same cause: to reach the lost for Jesus. Let's join together and reach the lost for Jesus.

00:13:58.663 --> 00:14:09.265
Regardless of what our beliefs are, you may believe in the baptism of the Holy Spirit, you may not; you may believe in the gifts and signs and wonders, you may not—I don't know.

00:14:09.266 --> 00:14:13.394
We do. But does that make me better than you? No, it just makes me hungry.

00:14:13.394 --> 00:14:20.911
I'm hungry and thirsty. We're seeking Him. I know you're hungry and thirsty and seeking Him in your way.

00:14:20.912 --> 00:14:28.958
But my goodness, folks, what could we do if we joined together? The devil has divided us.

00:14:28.959 --> 00:14:45.085
The devil has made us think, "Well, you're this and I'm that."No, I believe it's just like racial things—"Well, you're Black, I'm white; you're Mexican, I'm white; you're browner, I'm redder."Whatever.

00:14:45.086 --> 00:14:57.759
We're all the same blood. We have the same color of blood. My organs would work in your body. Skin shouldn't matter. We're brothers and sisters.

00:14:57.760 --> 00:15:07.119
It's time to put away our petty differences and rise up and be what God has called us to be: a body.

00:15:07.120 --> 00:15:15.720
You may be the hand, but I might be the foot. Either way, we work together and we make something beautiful happen.

00:15:15.721 --> 00:15:23.636
Like the Bible says, even the parts that are not seen are sometimes the most vital.

00:15:23.637 --> 00:15:30.117
It's just so important because I'm telling you all, I have such a hunger and anticipation.

00:15:30.118 --> 00:15:38.799
And he told me, "Brandon, I'm going to shake this world like it's never been shaken before.

00:15:38.800 --> 00:15:42.632
You're about to see things that you never thought you would see.

00:15:42.633 --> 00:15:51.838
It will be with earthquakes, volcanoes, and signs in the heavens.

00:15:51.839 --> 00:16:11.913
It's going to shake the ones that are pretending to be awake."He said, "Brandon, for my remnant doesn't even have an urgency, and I am going to bring a great urgency to my body.

00:16:11.914 --> 00:16:30.479
The ones that are standing in the way will be removed. I will bring up the ones that are hungry, thirsty, and desperate for me, and I will use you mightily in these last days.

00:16:30.480 --> 00:16:38.529
For the ones that have a religious nose to the sky will either go by the graveside or they're going to be removed.

00:16:38.530 --> 00:16:49.439
I don't know how, but he told me they will be removed and I will bring forth the new Davids—the ones that will just say yes.

00:16:49.440 --> 00:17:00.373
God's just looking for a yielded yes. I've said it, and I'll say it again: God's just looking for somebody who says yes.

00:17:00.374 --> 00:17:08.693
We came across this prophecy. Sister Billie was talking about this at the conference, and Diana, this is from Brother Kenneth E.

00:17:08.694 --> 00:17:21.471
Hagin. He gave this word back, I don't know how long ago, but it goes alongside what I'm trying to tell you. He even saw what I've tried to tell you all.

00:17:21.472 --> 00:17:30.318
Tapping into the spirit realm, tapping into the river, will be like taking a breath where it's been so hard to get into it before in the past.

00:17:30.319 --> 00:17:36.109
It's going to be so easy. We're just going to jump right into those rivers.

00:17:36.110 --> 00:17:51.802
Holy Ghost flow. Holy Ghost rivers are coming in a mighty rushing wind. The sound of a mighty rushing wind. This was exciting.

00:17:51.803 --> 00:18:01.509
Diana reads so much better than me, and I said, "Baby, will you read this for me?"Okay, so this is from Kenneth E.

00:18:01.510 --> 00:18:11.232
Hagin, and it was from 1983. Oh, 1983. Yeah, 1983. It's amazing. I wanted to read this.

00:18:11.233 --> 00:18:17.105
Hopefully, I can do it justice because it's amazing and very powerful.

00:18:17.106 --> 00:18:23.596
In this move, you have not seen the revival of divine healing that you're about to see.

00:18:23.597 --> 00:18:30.876
Praise God, y'all. Oh, yes. You saw those that I raised up. You've seen men and women mightily used of my spirit.

00:18:30.877 --> 00:18:37.792
I sent them forth as a pilot program to try to train you, but many just looked at them and lifted them up.

00:18:37.793 --> 00:18:45.077
Some of them were lifted up in pride and the anointing left them. Right? See, deflect. Deflect.

00:18:45.078 --> 00:18:50.589
That's what the Holy Spirit told us when he visited us: "We're going to work mightily together, but you're always to deflect.

00:18:50.590 --> 00:18:54.742
Don't let the pride in."Yes, that is it. I didn't hear him say that before.

00:18:54.743 --> 00:19:01.914
Yes, I'm sorry, I just—my goodness. And some became money-minded and lost the anointing.

00:19:01.915 --> 00:19:09.439
Money-minded. Pride and money. But there will arise a group in this day that's a brand new breed.

00:19:09.440 --> 00:19:20.548
They'll not be greedy of filthy lucre. They'll not be wanting to attract attention unto themselves.

00:19:20.549 --> 00:19:30.086
They would care less whether God uses me; they'd rather God use you. And God will not use just ministers; He'll use laymen.

00:19:30.087 --> 00:19:41.292
And there'll be a revival of divine healing such as you have not seen in your lifetime or read about or heard about, saith the Lord, and a revival of the supernatural.

00:19:41.293 --> 00:19:54.253
Not only the supernatural in casting out devils, not only the supernatural in healing the sick, not only the supernatural in speaking with other tongues, but the supernatural in the realm of the seen realm.

00:19:54.254 --> 00:20:02.719
Men will see the glory of God. A cloud will hang over certain congregations, even the church building, for days at a time.

00:20:02.720 --> 00:20:08.336
And everybody that passes by, sinner and saint alike, will say, 'Well, what in the world is that?

00:20:08.337 --> 00:20:14.399
I've never seen anything like that.'And there will be in other places the fire of the spirit.

00:20:14.400 --> 00:20:25.313
Oh yes, in the spirit realm, some of us have seen it; we've been conscious of the fire of God. But the fire will actually come into manifestation.

00:20:25.314 --> 00:20:32.879
And there'll be people, sinners as well as saints, that will see fire all over the heads of the people.

00:20:32.880 --> 00:20:50.611
They'll be driving down the street or down the highway and they'll see fire on top of the buildings and they'll come and say, 'What does all of this mean?'But you see, the Lord will use signs of His presence to bring people in the last days into the fullness of His spirit and into full salvation.

00:20:50.611 --> 00:20:57.252
And signs, signs—what kinds of signs? Miraculous things in the realm of the spirit.

00:20:57.253 --> 00:21:00.719
And then they'll be manifested in the realm of the physical.

00:21:00.720 --> 00:21:06.319
And the glory of God will fall. And the power of God will be in manifestation.

00:21:06.320 --> 00:21:12.956
And men and women too will even be transported like Philip was and found in another place.

00:21:12.957 --> 00:21:21.794
And great, great, great shall be the reward thereof. For the Lord God is the same God today as He was yesterday.

00:21:21.795 --> 00:21:30.185
His power has not diminished, and His name is still the same. Today He can make the iron axe head float.

00:21:30.186 --> 00:21:36.185
Today He can divide the river just for two men to cross over to the other side.

00:21:36.186 --> 00:21:42.646
Today He can feed 5,000 with a little boy's lunch. He is the miracle-working God.

00:21:42.647 --> 00:21:49.042
Brag on Him. Lift Him up. Draw attention unto Him. Tell about how great He is.

00:21:49.043 --> 00:21:53.249
Get up in faith and tell about what great things He's going to do.

00:21:53.250 --> 00:21:57.664
And He'll move and keep His word with you. And many shall be astonished.

00:21:57.665 --> 00:22:05.381
But the greatest miracle of all is that there'll be so many fish caught in the net that the nets can't hold them.

00:22:05.382 --> 00:22:10.296
The Lord said, 'Get a big net. Brandon, it's time to get a bigger net.

00:22:10.297 --> 00:22:16.460
You've got to catch them because they're coming in hot.'And I saw them coming in really fast. And I was like a catcher's mitt for a fastball coming in.

00:22:16.461 --> 00:22:21.488
He said, 'Catch them because they're coming in fast.'Brandon, what's about the shaking that's going to awaken?

00:22:21.489 --> 00:22:30.234
They're coming in fast. Are you ready? Go. There won't be church houses enough to hold the people.

00:22:30.235 --> 00:22:38.397
Amen. Amen. For the purpose of all is that you may be fishers of men.

00:22:38.398 --> 00:22:43.172
Hallelujah. Quit fishing in your bathtub. There's not any fish in your own bathtub.

00:22:43.173 --> 00:22:54.980
Go out where the fish are and throw out the net—not the hook, the net—and pull it in and bring them in. And the glory of the Lord shall shine and the end shall come.

00:22:54.981 --> 00:23:07.296
And you'll stand in the place, yes, many of you that stand here, including myself, will stand in the place of ministry that you've not stood in before, and will stand in the place that's been ordained for you from the foundation of the earth.

00:23:07.297 --> 00:23:24.812
And if it were to be told to you, if we were able to tell you in human language that which will transpire in some of your lives and some of our lives who are here just now, your mind would not be able to comprehend it.

00:23:24.812 --> 00:23:31.476
As you say, speaking in the human vernacular, it would almost blow your mind.

00:23:31.477 --> 00:23:35.723
But you'll see it. You'll rejoice in it. You'll be glad of it.

00:23:35.724 --> 00:23:40.674
It's just out there a little ways in front of you. Be faithful.

00:23:40.675 --> 00:23:48.878
That was in 1983. So it's not a little ways anymore, folks. No, we're there.

00:23:48.879 --> 00:24:00.082
I mean, what is that, 41 years ago? Yep. Praise God, folks. It's just out there a little ways in front of you.

00:24:00.083 --> 00:24:05.678
Be faithful. Be joyous. And rejoice in the Lord always, and He'll bring it to pass.

00:24:05.679 --> 00:24:13.944
Many shall go and tell the story and His great glory show. The power of God in manifestation shall be the gifts of the spirit.

00:24:13.945 --> 00:24:18.715
The manifestation of His spirit into full potential shall come the ministry gifts.

00:24:18.716 --> 00:24:25.670
The apostle and the prophet, the evangelist and pastor and teacher too shall flow as one.

00:24:25.671 --> 00:24:34.412
One body in the spirit. Hallelujah. Shall go forth to conquer and to do His deeds and great shall be the reward thereof.

00:24:34.413 --> 00:24:39.911
Thank Him. Glory to God. Now, let me give you further wisdom and advice.

00:24:39.912 --> 00:24:46.911
Being conscious of a mighty move in your spirit, wanting and desiring to do the will of God, but don't try to do it yourself.

00:24:46.912 --> 00:24:52.312
Just learn to relax and to flow with the spirit. Don't try to figure it out in your head.

00:24:52.313 --> 00:24:56.914
What does He want me to do? Just learn to relax and flow with the spirit.

00:24:56.915 --> 00:25:08.531
It'll take care of itself. You don't have to worry. I know there's something He wants me to do. Fine. Just keep on praying and just flow with the spirit.

00:25:08.532 --> 00:25:19.868
You'll not come into the full potential of what God has for you tomorrow, next week, or next month.

00:25:19.869 --> 00:25:27.423
